UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1816
1 Section 3. The members of the Senate encourage the citizens of the
2 Commonwealth to support, promote, and participate in mentorship opportunities that help
3 young people succeed and strengthen Kentucky’s communities.
4 Section 4. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
5 Resolution to Senator Shelley Funke Frommeyer for delivery.
